title: Urbanization in Jamaica 2018
yAxis: Share of urban population in total population
summary: In general Share of urban population in total population has stayed the same over the Year.
Share of urban population in total population is slightly increasing from 2010 to 2017.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2016 and 2017.
The highest Share of urban population in total population, of value 55.38 was reached at Year 2017
The lowest Share of urban population in total population, of value 53.74 was reported at Year 2010
